snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda GBC - Beta v0.29 (Windows & Linux) Longplay
snippet.description:
Download(s) OneDrive - Beta v0.29
Windows: https://1drv.ms/u/s!Antze46_KH6j62LeKvxUb8fp-bUC?e=fHICKa
Linux: https://1drv.ms/u/s!Antze46_KH6j62OrwLVVw3DpYn0N?e=ijDWD1

Currently working on: Continue, save, retry menu. Player death.

Item Drop Infographic: https://i.imgur.com/cKRfGtZ.png

Beta v0.29 Changes
------------------
Fixed music in Level-1 with Wallmasters and respawn.

Beta v0.28 Changes
------------------
Wallmasters take you to beginning of Level.
When you die, game saves, then resarts either at Area 120 or Entrance of Level.
Retry counter increments when player dies.
Old man in Level-1 attack fixed.
